trans-unit.source: Defines the routing behavior, which is used to configure the destination endpoints, filters and filtering options to be used during routing.
trans-unit.target: Define o comportamento de roteamento, que é usado para configurar os pontos de extremidade de destino, filtros e opções de filtragem a serem usados durante o roteamento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingBehavior> registers all of the run-time components used by the routing service, including the channel initializer, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.SoapProcessingBehavior>, and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingExtension>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingBehavior> registra todos os componentes de tempo de execução usados pelo serviço de roteamento, incluindo o inicializador de canal, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.SoapProcessingBehavior>e o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingExtension>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingBehavior" /> class with the specified routing configuration.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingBehavior" /> com a configuração de roteamento especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingBehavior> registers all of the run-time components used by the routing service, including the channel initializer, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.SoapProcessingBehavior>, and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingExtension>, which uses the specified <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingBehavior> registra todos os componentes de tempo de execução usados pelo serviço de roteamento, incluindo o inicializador de canal, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.SoapProcessingBehavior>e o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingExtension>, que usa especificado <xref:System.ServiceModel.Routing.RoutingConfiguration>.
